This file documents the code for replication of experiment results.
The following files are present.

mse replication.R: experiments on mse of mean estimation model and squared loss model

normal plot.R: experiments on asymptotic normality of different weighted averaged SGD

plots of different weights.R: numerical studies on visualizing different weighting schemes for the expectile regression model

high dimensional MSE.R: experiments on d=100 and d=500 linear regression

coverage.ipynb: experiments on the empirical coverage of confidence intervals
